# Stoney Maloney – Shopify Liquid Theme

- **Liquid** – All markup and logic
- **CSS** – Custom styles (no Tailwind, no Bootstrap)
- **JavaScript** – Vanilla JS only, no React/frameworks
- **100% Shopify-hosted** – No Firebase, Vercel, or external hosting

## Conventions

- Use sections for merchant-editable content (header, footer, hero, product grids)
- Use snippets for reusable Liquid (pagination, icons, etc.)
- JSON templates for page structure (index, collection, product, page)
- Section schemas define theme editor settings
- Store: stoney-maloney-usa.myshopify.com
- Design: clean, minimal, high-end aesthetic
